e dudas. PD: DespuÃ©s de terminar las animaciones  aumenta el precio, asÃ­ que aprovechen.", "appid": "108600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198146742547", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1574164800.0}
